snippet: A conservative group on Tuesday sued a county clerk of courts, Orlando's mayor and a judge in an effort to stop them from helping same-sex couples get married in Florida next week....

headline.print_headline: Florida Group Tries to Stop Gay Marriages
headline.main: Florida Group Tries to Stop Gay Marriages

lead_paragraph: A conservative group on Tuesday sued a county clerk of courts, Orlando's mayor and a judge in an effort to stop them from helping same-sex couples get married in Florida next week.
